{"tid":466613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國人食屎原來係有淵源","createTime":"2017-11-12T17:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T16:15:27.000Z","uid":52023,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0ae0ac2910a10b8a7a886ba61ae6721fd624c2","tid":466613,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:10:41.000Z","msg":"朝鮮傳統製法為在竹筒上割開一個小洞，將松葉塞入洞裡並放置在廁所中；經過3-4個月之後，竹筒裡就會殘留下清澈的液體。將該液體混入馬格利熟成之後，糞酒便正式完成。另有一速成法則為直接將糞便加入酒中，等待3日便能製成，是稱「野人乾酒」（야인건술）；但據說這種速成型的糞酒不但很臭、難以入口外，藥效還十分薄弱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xbzo0DBB4Ys\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXbzo0DBB4Ys&d=KOpSeH6kBKY0KqQK2ZYqbp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b3aa5827\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xbzo0DBB4Ys</a><br />\n哇屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989f91c2f228521de2a726bde7d25b466676a937","tid":466613,"uid":43042,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"日本仔食屎先係始祖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6279995a7f298d29053127e308fd1c03bfe8b81b","tid":466613,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f257ff4d34c1d09cfaaeb17340a972e0e7e7e1","tid":466613,"uid":19557,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:55:28.000Z","msg":"泡菜真係正一食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e64ae3aba646a10b37330ea22a863e67a5c1123","tid":466613,"uid":49955,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:58:38.000Z","msg":"支國人好鐘意靠翻譯片黎製造仇恨<br />\n睇少D"},{"pid":"e6378744433e03808217a43ea0158792244cc55f","tid":466613,"uid":55913,